title.narrative: Joint Liaison Office in Nay Pyi Taw

description.narrative: This activity (Joint Liaison Office in Nay Pyi Taw) is a component of Accelerated Reform Facility (ARF) reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Other bilateral donor' and a budget of £419,223. This component benefits Myanmar, and works in the following sector(s): Public sector policy and administrative management. , with the following implementing partners: Australian Aid, Department of Foreign Affairs and Trade - Australia. The start date is 16-08-2012 and the end date is 30-06-2022.
